Game : Speed Devils 
Date : 2003/08/19 
Video: PAL
Ripped by: DCP
Rip notes: downsampled some FMVs

High stakes gambling and custom car racing through Satan's playground ! 
* 12 brutal tracks : race through crowded cities, snow covered mountains and active volcanoes.
* Take on UFOs, rockslides and a giant fist-smashing ape.
* Challenge 17 diabolical drivers through championships, vendettas and high-stakes duels. 
* Tons af alternative routes ; can you find them all ? 
* Race old-school muscle machines or exotic european cars. 
* Authentic repairable damage, buy and upgrade cars. 